CHTL (Chtholly HyperText Language) Compiler
A modern dual-language hypertext compiler with innovative architecture.

Features:
- Dual-language separation architecture (CHTL + CHTL JS)
- Precise code segmentation with variable-length slicing
- ANTLR-based CSS and JavaScript compilation
- Intelligent code merger for fragment-to-complete code conversion
- Complete UTF-8 support for Chinese programming
- Extensible CJMOD API for unlimited syntax extensions
- Enterprise-grade performance and optimization

This project represents a significant technological milestone in compiler design,
demonstrating innovation, completeness, rigor, and high standards in modern
software development.